snippet.title: Mother of 19-year-old on Titan submersible speaks out
snippet.description:
The United States Coast Guard says it’s convening a marine board of investigators to figure out what caused the deep-sea implosion of OceanGate’s Titan submersible. Meanwhile, the wife and mother of two of the passengers is opening up about her last moments with them. NBC’s Emilie Ikeda reports for TODAY.
